claim.claim-text:
1. In a gaming machine having a housing which includes a front housing portion defining a game control surface for game controls, an extendable bet button comprising: 
a push button switch; 
an elongated electrical cable connected to said push button switch, said elongated electrical cable carried within the interior of said front housing portion in a non-extended position; 
an aperture provided in a game control surface for carrying said push button switch in a non-extended position and enabling said cable to be pulled therethrough in an extended position to enable said push button to be moved remotely from said game control surface.
